Note:
RUNA Traceback Library: Performance Correlation and Root Cause Analysis Module

Revolutionary performance correlation system that combines stack trace analysis with
precise timing data to identify root causes of performance issues. Integrates hardware
timing, profiling data, and call stack analysis to provide comprehensive performance
insights with automated root cause identification and optimization recommendations.

Key Features:
- Performance correlation analysis between stack traces and timing data
- Root cause identification through multi-dimensional performance analysis
- Hardware counter correlation with execution patterns
- Memory usage correlation with call stack patterns - Lock contention analysis with thread synchronization patterns
- I/O performance correlation with system call patterns
- Cache miss correlation with data access patterns
- Branch prediction correlation with code execution flows
- Automatic performance regression detection and analysis
- Multi-threaded performance bottleneck identification
- Performance trend analysis with predictive modeling
- Optimization recommendation engine based on correlation patterns
:End Note

Import module "traceback/traceback" as Traceback
Import module "traceback/temporal" as Temporal
Import module "time/core" as TimeCore
Import module "time/hardware" as HardwareTimer
Import module "time/profiler" as Profiler
Import module "collections" as Collections

Note: Performance Correlation Types and Analysis Framework
Type called "PerformanceCorrelationSession":
    session_id as String
    temporal_session as Temporal.TemporalDebugSession
    profiler_session as Profiler.ProfilerSession
    correlation_config as CorrelationConfig
    performance_correlations as List[PerformanceCorrelation]
    root_cause_analyses as List[RootCauseAnalysis]
    optimization_recommendations as List[OptimizationRecommendation]
    regression_analyses as List[RegressionAnalysis]
    correlation_matrices as List[CorrelationMatrix]
    session_statistics as CorrelationStatistics
    is_active as Boolean
    metadata as Dictionary[String, Any]

Type called "CorrelationConfig":
    enable_hardware_correlation as Boolean
    enable_memory_correlation as Boolean
    enable_thread_correlation as Boolean
    enable_io_correlation as Boolean
    correlation_window_ms as Integer
    statistical_significance_threshold as Float
    regression_detection_sensitivity as Float
    root_cause_confidence_threshold as Float
    optimization_aggressiveness as OptimizationLevel
    real_time_correlation as Boolean
    metadata as Dictionary[String, Any]

Type OptimizationLevel is:
